{"tid":441132,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"要點樣對一個男仔示好","createTime":"2017-10-19T11:24:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T02:06:52.000Z","uid":83836,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9ff08d0fa1b408b3b48977d5d7788d781ea9fddb","tid":441132,"uid":83836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:24:14.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我係一個對男仔會內向既絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為某d原因，每個禮拜都會有一堂坐係一個本身就對佢有好感既男仔隔離<br />\n上堂都會傾下計講下on9野都幾開心（不過多數都係佢講我笑）<br />\n但係一落左堂就冇哂交集，平時有其他堂會一齊上，但唔會特別坐佢隔離<br />\n想請問各位神通廣大既連登巴絲認為女仔應該點對男仔示好呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 a0，未知佢有女朋友未<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f605c8ea967e6366b02119470e82b62b2399f2","tid":441132,"uid":116705,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:26:48.000Z","msg":"一手渣落去佢條J度"},{"pid":"6b78ff4e8a28b2e32b60de565cd233a1fb3314af","tid":441132,"uid":82929,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:30:29.000Z","msg":"追住佢條撚含"},{"pid":"759ff9415284b1f9fcb89f371eab7d93868fb076","tid":441132,"uid":83836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:43:58.000Z","msg":"認真post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917928395b4ecc516b82a66ef789aa2ac5540afd","tid":441132,"uid":26414,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:45:06.000Z","msg":"捉住佢隻手揸落你個波度"},{"pid":"b1ee80fac7446ce1d47a7e58ac3b42b9b8088b7f","tid":441132,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T12:05:13.000Z","msg":"問佢拎電話"},{"pid":"0f53c680e36435224f470c1746dbb0626f044329","tid":441132,"uid":128364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor